<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">5</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">18</span>日<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19:30</span></span></p>
