</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> <span style="font-size: medium;"><a href="http://www.chinacno.org/images/2013/05/yyt/05-18-poster.jpg" onclick="window.open('http://www.chinacno.org/images/2013/05/yyt/05-18-poster.jpg','','left='+(screen.availWidth/2-0)+',top='+(screen.availHeight/2-0)+'');return false;">宣传海报</a></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、女声独唱《对花歌》                                                                           郑源词曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《愿亲人早日养好伤》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                   </span>电影《沂蒙颂》插曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                    演唱：李研心</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、男声独唱《山歌唱出好兆头》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                              </span>郑南词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>饶荣发曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                       《想家的时候》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                       </span>邵斌词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>王立平曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演唱：周伟</span></p>
