<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        演奏：张璐(香港龙音杯民乐大赛获奖者)</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、男声独唱《母亲》                                                                 车行词  戚建波曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《红星照我去战斗》                               电影《闪闪的红星》插曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演唱：赵海风</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、女声独唱《女儿情》                                                   电视剧《西游记》插曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《梨花颂》                                                          翁思再词 杨乃林曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演唱：唐文娟</span></p>
