<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《鸿雁》                                                           根据蒙古民歌改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                       演唱：赵健</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、男女声对唱《载歌载舞》                                                       车行词 戚建波曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                           《家和万事兴》                                    石顺义、郁钧剑词 刘青曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                  演唱：唐文娟 周伟</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、女声独唱《太湖美》                                                               任红举词 龙飞曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《说聊斋》                                                              乔羽词 王立平曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                      演唱：郭春梅</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九、男女声对唱《龙船调》                                                                        湖北民歌</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                           《刘海砍樵》                                                                湖南花鼓戏</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                 演唱：赵海风 郭春梅</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、笛子独奏《鹧鸪飞》                                                                          赵松庭曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《扬鞭催马运粮忙》                                                          魏显忠曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                演奏：丁晓逵(中央电视台民族器乐大赛获奖者)  </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、男女声对唱《婚誓》                                              电影《芦笙恋歌》插曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                《为了谁》                                                 邹友开词 孟庆云曲</span></p>
